    <Name>Ultimate Civilization</Name>
    <Teaser>A civilization that has replaced all regular units with the best available unique unit. It is the best mankind has to offer.</Teaser>
    <Description>A civilization that has replaced all regular units with the best available unique unit, &amp; all regular buildings with the best available unique building.  It is the best mankind has to offer. You'll have the bonus traits of any civilization that would otherwise prove you inferior. You can also build the Terrace Farm, Polder &amp; Kasbah.

A great civilization to play on Deity difficulty.

