Traits

Ingenuity
Receive free Great Scientist when you discover Writing. Earn Great Scientists 50% faster

ScholarsOfTheJadeHall
+2 science for all specialists &amp; for all Great Person tile improvements. Receive a tech boost each time a scientific building/Wonder is built in your capital

TreasuresOfNinevah
When a city is conquered, gain a free tech already discovered by its owner (cannot be gained through trade deal, &amp; only once per city)

Iklwa
Melee units cost 50% less maintenance. All promotions require 25% less experience

Art of War
The Great General combat bonus is increased by 15%, and their spawn rate is increased by 50%

Bushido
Units fight as though they were at full strength even when damaged. +1 Culture from each Fishing Boat, +2 Culture from each Atoll

ScourgeOfGod
Raze Cities at 2x speed. Borrow City names from other Civs. Start with Animal Husbandry tech. +1 Production on Pasture

FurorTeutonicus
Upon defeating a Barbarian unit in an encampment, there is a 67% they join your side (still get gold). Pay 25% less for land unit maintenance

BarbaryCorsairs
All melee naval units have the Prize Ships promotion, allowing them to capture defeated ships. Pay only 1/3 usual cost for naval unit maintenance

GreatExpanse
Founded cities start with additional territory. Units receive a combat bonus when fighting within their own territory

ManifestDestiny
All land military units have +1 sight. Buy tiles for 1/2 price

SunNeverSets
+2 Movement for all naval units. Receives 1 extra Spy

Partial Siberian Riches
Strategic Resources provide +1 Production

MonumentBuilders
+20% Production towards Wonder construction

AchaemenidLegacy
Golden Ages last 50% longer. During a Golden Age, units receive +1 Movement &amp; +10% Strength in combat

GloryOfRome
+25% Production towards any buildings that already exist in the Capital

GreatWarpath
Units move through Forest &amp; Jungle in friendly territory as if it is Road. These tiles can be used to establish Trade Routes upon researching The Wheel

GreatAndeanRoad
Units ignore terrain costs when moving into any tile with Hills. No maintenance costs for improvements in Hills; 1/2 cost elsewhere

PhoenicianHeritage
Units may cross mountains after the first Khan is earned, taking 50 HP damage if they end a turn on a mountain

VikingFury
Embarked units have +1 Movement &amp; pay just 1 movement point to move from sea to land. Melee units pay no movement point cost to pillage

RiverWarlord
Receive 3x Gold from Barbarian encampments &amp; pillaging Cities. Embarked units can defend themselves

Sacrificial Captives
Gains Culture for the empire from each enemy unit killed.

Solidarity
Receive a free Social Policy when you advance to the next era
...</Description>
